<span id="freeTextContainer7246004704895862708">Don&apos;t normally take the time to leave reviews, but this one earned it. I seriously couldn&apos;t put Safe &amp; Sound down. Took me less than 48 hours to read it. A girlfriend of mine suggested I check this book out since I&apos;m such a big Nicholas Sparks fan. She was spot on! Although, I&apos;d say this author was slightly less sappy. Went on a serious emotional roller coaster with Jill and was consistently surprised. Just when I thought I had it figured out, the story would take a different turn. Loved. it. Ho</span>
  <span id="freeText7246004704895862708" style="display:none">Don't normally take the time to leave reviews, but this one earned it. I seriously couldn't put Safe &amp; Sound down. Took me less than 48 hours to read it. A girlfriend of mine suggested I check this book out since I'm such a big Nicholas Sparks fan. She was spot on! Although, I'd say this author was slightly less sappy. Went on a serious emotional roller coaster with Jill and was consistently surprised. Just when I thought I had it figured out, the story would take a different turn. Loved. it. Hoping this author gets her next book out quickly! :)</span>
