<span id="freeTextContainer9811165144771004696">T.S. Krupa was born in New Haven, CT. She was raised in a blended Polish-American household. T.S. Krupa earned her Bachelor&apos;s degree at Franklin Pierce University, Master&apos;s at Texas Tech University and her Doctorate of Education from North Carolina State University . She played field hockey at in college and continues to be involved by coaching a local club team. She currently resides in North Car</span>
  <span id="freeText9811165144771004696" style="display:none">T.S. Krupa was born in New Haven, CT. She was raised in a blended Polish-American household. T.S. Krupa earned her Bachelor's degree at Franklin Pierce University, Master's at Texas Tech University and her Doctorate of Education from North Carolina State University . She played field hockey at in college and continues to be involved by coaching a local club team. She currently resides in North Carolina with her husband, daughter and dog. <br /><br />T.S. Krupa is a SBR Media author and has released four books to date: Safe &amp; Sound, On the Edge, The Ten Year Reunion, and Big City Dreams. </span>
